<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 06:15:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>固态：电动汽车巨头追逐电池的“圣杯”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/solid-state-ev-giants-chase-holy-grail-batteries-2024-01-16/</link><description>固态电池有望为下一代电动汽车提供更多的能量存储、更长的行驶里程和更快的充电速度。然而，尽管经过数十年的研究和数十亿美元的投资，它们的未来仍然显得难以捉摸。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 06:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/solid-state-ev-giants-chase-holy-grail-batteries-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国经济陷入困境，李克强总理将在达沃斯发表讲话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-premier-li-address-davos-its-economy-struggles-2024-01-16/</link><description>中国总理李强将于周二在达沃斯向全球投资者和政界人士发表讲话，目前北京正努力应对疫情后复苏缓慢和房地产市场低迷的问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 06:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-premier-li-address-davos-its-economy-struggles-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：大众汽车及其竞争对手正在攻克固态电池难题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/volkswagen-rivals-plug-away-solid-state-battery-puzzle-2024-01-16/</link><description>大众汽车与美国初创公司 QuantumScape 合作开发“固态”电动汽车电池的计划一直被拖延，但该公司正在扩大网络，以追求可能改变游戏规则的技术。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 06:03:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/volkswagen-rivals-plug-away-solid-state-battery-puzzle-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>太平洋国家齐聚中国讨论海军问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/pacific-nations-meet-china-discuss-naval-issues-2024-01-16/</link><description>官方媒体称，日本、俄罗斯和美国等太平洋沿岸国家的海军官员将于周二在中国东部城市南京举行会议，讨论更新有关意外遭遇的规则等问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 05:56:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/pacific-nations-meet-china-discuss-naval-issues-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>新疆雪崩致约1000名游客被困</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/about-1000-tourists-trapped-chinas-xinjiang-after-avalanches-2024-01-16/</link><description>据国家电视台周二报道，中国西北部新疆地区遭遇雪崩，积雪高达数米，多变的天气阻碍了撤离，目前约有 1000 名游客仍被困在一个偏远的度假村。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 05:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/about-1000-tourists-trapped-chinas-xinjiang-after-avalanches-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国在台湾就职前夕进行等待游戏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-plays-waiting-game-run-up-taiwan-inauguration-2024-01-16/</link><description>中国对台湾当选总统赖清德上周末的胜利反应冷淡，这表明一些分析人士认为，这是他上任前四个月不安的开始，而北京方面在此之前小心行事。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 05:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-plays-waiting-game-run-up-taiwan-inauguration-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园预计2024年中国房地产市场将持续疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-expects-china-property-market-remain-weak-2024-2024-01-16/</link><description>中国最大的私人房地产开发商碧桂园，2007.HK 高层表示，预计 2024 年房地产市场将持续疲软，该公司可能面临更多“严峻”挑战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 04:38:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-expects-china-property-market-remain-weak-2024-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>台积电Q4利润下滑23% 今年重点关注需求反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmcs-q4-profit-slide-23-focus-rebounding-demand-this-year-2024-01-16/</link><description>台积电周四预计第四季度利润下降 23%，但分析师预计，由于需求反弹，今年的增长将有所改善。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:43:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmcs-q4-profit-slide-23-focus-rebounding-demand-this-year-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>马科斯总统祝贺台湾黎智英后菲​​律宾重申“一个中国政策”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-reaffirms-one-china-policy-after-president-marcos-congratulates-2024-01-16/</link><description>在菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯向台湾新领导人赖清德表示祝贺后，菲律宾外交部周二重申了该国的“一个中国政策”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-reaffirms-one-china-policy-after-president-marcos-congratulates-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>美国谴责瑙鲁“不幸”放弃台湾，并对中国的承诺发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/naurus-decision-break-ties-with-taiwan-unfortunate-us-official-2024-01-16/</link><description>周二，负责处理与台湾非正式关系的机构负责人的美国官员谴责瑙鲁在选举后不久做出与台北断绝关系的“不幸”决定，并警告说北京的承诺往往没有兑现。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 02:10:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/naurus-decision-break-ties-with-taiwan-unfortunate-us-official-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>格鲁吉亚执政党领导人访华推动深化双边关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/georgias-ruling-party-leader-visits-china-push-deeper-ties-2024-01-15/</link><description>据格鲁吉亚媒体报道，格鲁吉亚执政党领导人周一开始对中国进行为期六天的访问，这个欧盟候选成员国寻求深化与北京的关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 14:36:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/georgias-ruling-party-leader-visits-china-push-deeper-ties-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>玩具制造商从中国转移并非易事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/toy-manufacturers-shift-china-is-no-childs-play-2024-01-15/</link><description>正在努力应对中国成本飙升的玩具制造商在将生产转移到更便宜的地方时没有找到简单的选择。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 13:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/toy-manufacturers-shift-china-is-no-childs-play-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国与瑞士签署扩大贸易宣言</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-switzerland-sign-declaration-with-view-expanding-trade-2024-01-15/</link><description>瑞士政府表示，李强总理会见瑞士总统后，中国和瑞士周一签署了一份联合声明，同意深化合作伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 13:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-switzerland-sign-declaration-with-view-expanding-trade-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：胡塞武装袭击暴露了中国在红海的商业利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-attacks-expose-chinas-commercial-stakes-red-sea-2024-01-15/</link><description>中国呼吁停止对红海民用船只的袭击，这种袭击极大地扩大了哈马斯与以色列的冲突，并使北京在苏伊士运河沿岸的商业利益面临风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-attacks-expose-chinas-commercial-stakes-red-sea-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜黑客与犯罪分子在东南亚共享洗钱网络 - 联合国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-hackers-criminals-share-money-laundering-networks-southeast-asia-un-2024-01-15/</link><description>根据周一发布的联合国报告，朝鲜黑客正在与东南亚的欺诈者和毒贩共享洗钱和地下银行网络，赌场和加密货币交易所成为有组织犯罪的主要场所。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-hackers-criminals-share-money-laundering-networks-southeast-asia-un-2024-01-15/</guid></item></channel></rss>